<section class="what-is">
  <h2>what is crux?</h2>
  <p>
    <code>.crux/</code> is a directory that stores everything your AI learns —
    corrections, patterns, session state, safety rules.
    it travels with you. no matter what tool you use.
  </p>
  <pre><code>$ crux switch opencode</code></pre>
  <p>
    start in Claude Code at work. pick up in OpenCode at home.
    same knowledge. same corrections. same context.
  </p>
</section>

